headline: Can CrowdStrike Stock Keep Moving Higher in 2025?
summary: CrowdStrike's all-in-one Falcon cybersecurity platform is increasingly popular for businesses, and it has a substantial long-term growth runway.  CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) is one of the world's biggest cybersecurity companies.  With that said, investors who are willing to take a longer-term view could still reap significant rewards by owning a slice of CrowdStrike.
